---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ContentPage from '../components/ContentPage.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure | Pet Care Blog"
  description="Important information about affiliate links and how we earn revenue to support our content."
>
  <ContentPage title="Affiliate Disclosure" updated="January 2026">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-0 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">Our Commitment to Transparency</h2>
    <p>
      At Pet Care Blog, we believe in complete transparency with our readers. This disclosure explains how we use affiliate links and how they may affect you.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">What Are Affiliate Links?</h2>
    <p>
      Some of the links on our website are "affiliate links." This means if you click on the link and purchase the item, Pet Care Blog will receive an affiliate commission at no extra cost to you.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">How This Affects Our Content</h2>
    <p>
      We want to be absolutely clear: <strong>affiliate relationships do not influence our editorial content</strong>. We only recommend products we genuinely believe will benefit you and your pets. Our recommendations are based on:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 my-4 space-y-2">
      <li>Thorough research and testing</li>
      <li>Expert veterinary input</li>
      <li>Real user reviews and feedback</li>
      <li>Our own experience with the products</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">Affiliate Partners</h2>
    <p>We participate in affiliate programs with the following companies:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 my-4 space-y-2">
      <li>Amazon Associates Program</li>
      <li>Chewy Affiliate Program</li>
      <li>Petco Affiliate Program</li>
      <li>Various pet product manufacturers</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">Amazon Associates Disclosure</h2>
    <p>
      Pet Care Blog is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program, an affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.com.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">Why We Use Affiliate Links</h2>
    <p>
      Running a quality website requires significant resources. Affiliate commissions help us:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 my-4 space-y-2">
      <li>Pay our expert writers and veterinary reviewers</li>
      <li>Maintain and improve our website</li>
      <li>Continue producing free, valuable content</li>
      <li>Keep the site ad-light for better user experience</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">Your Choice</h2>
    <p>
      You are never obligated to click on or purchase through our affiliate links. If you prefer, you can search for products directly on retailer websites. We appreciate when you do use our links, as it helps support our work at no additional cost to you.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">Questions?</h2>
    <p>
      If you have any questions about our affiliate relationships or how we choose products to recommend, please <a href="/contact" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">contact us</a>. We're happy to provide more information.
    </p>
  </ContentPage>
</BaseLayout>
